casebody.data:
Preusch, Respondent, v. Hill, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 16, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Bischoff, J.

Howe & Hummel, for appellant. D. Leventritt, for respondent.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
